short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export your Concordia Schedule to ical directly from Student center

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Winter 2018 - This Google Chrome extension allows you to export your Concordia Schedule to ical directly from Student center. Just click on the calendar icon while you are in Student Center and you should see an option to download your calendar to iCal format.
